                  .col.text-center.mb-1(style='flex:1 1 auto;')
                    a(href='https://pwc.csod.com/catalog/CustomPage.aspx?id=20003310#list-item-2', target='_blank')
                      img(src='https://pwc.csod.com/clientimg/pwc/welcome/TW/The%20PwC%20Professional/five.png', width='250')
                  .col(style='flex:1 1 auto;')
                    | In the face of global megatrends and economic uncertainty, now, more than ever,
                    | calls for a purposeful and disciplined development approach to ensure our learning
